ef=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframesRule\"><code>CSSKeyframesRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule\"><code>CSSMediaRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNamespaceRule\"><code>CSSNamespaceRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSPageRule\"><code>CSSPageRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSRuleList\"><code>CSSRuleList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleRule\"><code>CSSStyleRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleSheet\"><code>CSSStyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSSupportsRule\"><code>CSSSupportsRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CaretPosition\"><code>CaretPosition</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Screen\"><code>Screen</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StyleSheetList\"><code>StyleSheetList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TransitionEvent\"><code>TransitionEvent</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"概述","isH3":true,"content":"<p>返回当前样式表文件的 URI 地址。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"语法","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\"><em>uri</em> = stylesheet.href\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code>uri</code> 为一个字符串，包含了样式表文件的 URI 地址。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例子","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\"> // 在本机环境下\n &lt;html&gt;\n  &lt;head&gt;\n   &lt;link rel=\"StyleSheet\" href=\"example.css\" type=\"text/css\" /&gt;\n   &lt;script&gt;\n    function sref() {\n     alert(document.styleSheets[0].href);\n    }\n   &lt;/script&gt;\n  &lt;/head&gt;\n  &lt;body&gt;\n   &lt;div class=\"thunder\"&gt;Thunder&lt;/div&gt;\n   &lt;button onclick=\"sref()\"&gt;ss&lt;/button&gt;\n  &lt;/body&gt;\n &lt;/html&gt;\n// 弹出 \"file:////C:/Windows/Desktop/example.css\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"备注","isH3":true,"content":"<p>如果该样式表是一个外链样式表文件，则它的 href 属性值为样式表文件的 URI. 但如果该样式表是一个内联样式表，则它的 href 属性值为<code>null</code>.</p>\n\n<p>该属性在 Firefox, Opera, Google Chrome, Safari 中为只读属性，在 Internet Explorer 中可读可写。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"规范","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/2000/REC-DOM-Level-2-Style-20001113/stylesheets.html#StyleSheets-StyleSheet-href\" rel=\" noopener\">stylesheet.href </a></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"返回当前样式表文件的 URI 地址。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Stylesheet.href","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"stylesheet.href","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Stylesheet.href","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"StyleSheet.href","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"stylesheet.href","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/stylesheet/href","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/stylesheet/href/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet","title":"Sty